This package was put together by Bart Martens <bartm@debian.org>
on Thu, 06 Oct 2011 21:07:09 +0200.

The upstream source code was downloaded from:
http://xye.sourceforge.net/download.php

The upstream tarball was repackaged to remove these files :
  res/DejaVuSans-Bold.ttf
  res/DejaVuSans.ttf
  res/kye32_luminosity.png
  res/kye32.png
  res/kye_icon.png
  res/kye_luminosity.png
  res/kye.png
  res/kye.xcf
  res/xmaskye32.xml
  res/xmaskye.xml
  res/classic32.xml
  res/classic.xml
  res/XMASKye32_luminosity.png
  res/XMASKye32.png
  res/XMASKye_luminosity.png
  res/XMASKye.png

